review_res.text: I compared the first two unordered fruits in the line. Then put them in order below the pile. Then I compared the next unordered fruit in line to one of the ordered fruits. I tried to compare the new fruits to fruits that were in the middle of my ordered fruits, but since it was timed I also went with whatever was fastest to input. Then at the end I usually double checked my answers weighing all the fruits in line.
